*** 21,27 ****
  The following is basic information that all employees are expected to know:
  HM, King Terrorization, is the reigning monarch and Head-of-State.
  HM, Queen Rosanthe, is the Queen Consort, and the Prince of Wales is HRH, amazingconnor.
! The Royal Family act as HabboUK’s founders & RC, though they play a mostly ceremonial role.
  
  In the UK, there are Low-Rank & in-Command employees.
  LRs do not have any responsibilities but are expected to work at HQ stations whenever possible.
